  "title": "Tên lửa SOM-J đầu đạn 140kg, \u0027mắt thần AI\u0027 bay sát biển, \u0027xóa sổ\u0027 tàu chiến từ 275km",
  "url": "https://baomoi.com/ten-lua-som-j-dau-dan-140kg-mat-than-ai-bay-sat-bien-xoa-so-tau-chien-tu-275km-c53586123.epi",
  "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-main relative\"\u003e\n \u003ch1 class\u003d\"block text-[4rem] text-[var(--dark)] leading-[4.4rem] font-semibold mb-[5px]\"\u003eT\u0026ecirc;n lửa SOM-J đầu đạn 140kg, \u0027mắt thần AI\u0027 bay s\u0026aacute;t biển, \u0027x\u0026oacute;a sổ\u0027 t\u0026agrave;u chiến từ 275km\u003c/h1\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-meta flex items-center flex-wrap flex-row text-[1.3rem] leading-[2rem] font-normal text-[#999] truncate h-[30px] mb-[10px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;:not(:first-child)]:ml-[25px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"flex items-center\"\u003e\n   \u003ca href\u003d\"/bao-vietnamnet-vietnamnet-p23.epi\" class\u003d\"bm-card-source flex items-center shrink-0\" title\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o VietnamNet\"\u003e\n    \u003cfigure class\u003d\"image opacity-80 w-auto h-[16px]\" style\u003d\"width:56.25px;height:20px\" aria-label\u003d\"Logo nh\u0026agrave; xuất bản\"\u003e\n     \u003cpicture\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/26dc73b3aef047ae1ee1.png\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003csource srcset\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/26dc73b3aef047ae1ee1.png\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n      \u003cimg src\u003d\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/26dc73b3aef047ae1ee1.png\" alt\u003d\"B\u0026aacute;o VietnamNet\" width\u003d\"180\" height\u003d\"64\" /\u003e\n     \u003c/picture\u003e\n    \u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n   \u003cspan\u003e\u003cbutton class\u003d\"relative text-[14px] leading-[normal] font-normal text-center cursor-pointer normal-case border-0 transition-button disabled:shadow-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed follow-button flex items-center item-star ml-[10px]\" tabindex\u003d\"0\" type\u003d\"button\" title\u003d\"Theo d\u0026otilde;i \u0026quot;VietnamNet\u0026quot;\" aria-label\u003d\"Button\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003ctime datetime\u003d\"2025-10-25T23:30:00.000Z\"\u003e15 giờ trước\u003c/time\u003e\n  \u003ca href\u003d\"/ten-lua-som-j-dau-dan-140kg-mat-than-ai-bay-sat-bien-xoa-so-tau-chien-tu-275km-r53586123.epi\" class\u003d\"origin item-origin\" target\u003d\"_blank\" rel\u003d\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003ci class\u003d\"icon inline-block font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGốc\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n  \u003ci class\u003d\"bm-icon inline-block bg-[url(https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/bm-icon-2.0.3.png)] bg-[length:100px_4250px] align-middle bg-[0_-773px] w-[23px] h-[23px]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003ch3 class\u003d\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\"\u003eThổ Nhĩ Kỳ vừa khiến thế giới sửng sốt với cuộc thử nghiệm th\u0026agrave;nh c\u0026ocirc;ng t\u0026ecirc;n lửa h\u0026agrave;nh tr\u0026igrave;nh SOM-J - \u0027qu\u0026aacute;i vật\u0027 chống hạm nội địa c\u0026oacute; khả năng lướt s\u0026aacute;t mặt biển như b\u0026oacute;ng ma, tấn c\u0026ocirc;ng ch\u0026iacute;nh x\u0026aacute;c mục ti\u0026ecirc;u từ khoảng c\u0026aacute;ch 275km.\u003c/h3\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [\u0026amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;div]:mb-[15px]\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"body-block p-[20px] bg-[#eef8f9] italic [\u0026amp;\u0026gt;*:last-child]:mb-0\"\u003e\n   \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eMột \u0026quot;s\u0026aacute;t thủ v\u0026ocirc; h\u0026igrave;nh\u0026quot; lướt qua mặt biển với tốc độ cao dưới \u0026acirc;m thanh, sử dụng \u0026quot;mắt AI\u0026quot; hồng ngoại để kh\u0026oacute;a chặt mục ti\u0026ecirc;u từ 275km – đ\u0026oacute; ch\u0026iacute;nh l\u0026agrave; \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/ten-lua-tag1599.epi\"\u003et\u0026ecirc;n lửa\u003c/a\u003e SOM-J, kiệt t\u0026aacute;c c\u0026ocirc;ng nghệ Thổ Nhĩ Kỳ vừa \u0026quot;b\u0026ugrave;ng nổ\u0026quot; trong thử nghiệm ng\u0026agrave;y 13/10.\u003c/p\u003e\n   \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eKh\u0026ocirc;ng chỉ l\u0026agrave; vũ kh\u0026iacute;, t\u0026ecirc;n lửa SOM-J c\u0026ograve;n l\u0026agrave; minh chứng cho sự b\u0026ugrave;ng nổ tr\u0026iacute; tuệ nh\u0026acirc;n tạo (AI) v\u0026agrave; dẫn đường th\u0026ocirc;ng minh, biến kh\u0026ocirc;ng qu\u0026acirc;n \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/tho-nhi-ky-tag10897.epi\"\u003eThổ Nhĩ Kỳ\u003c/a\u003e th\u0026agrave;nh \u0026quot;ngư l\u0026ocirc;i bay\u0026quot; đ\u0026aacute;ng sợ nhất khu vực.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url(\u0027https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:350px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"M\u0026aacute;y bay chiến đấu được trang bị t\u0026ecirc;n lửa h\u0026agrave;nh tr\u0026igrave;nh SOM (ở giữa). Ảnh: TUBITAK SAGE\" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"350\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eM\u0026aacute;y bay chiến đấu được trang bị t\u0026ecirc;n lửa h\u0026agrave;nh tr\u0026igrave;nh SOM (ở giữa). Ảnh: TUBITAK SAGE\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"video-wrapper max-h-[80vh]\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:351.5625px;background:url(https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/player-default-03.png) no-repeat center center;background-size:cover\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eVideo: WION\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eT\u0026ecirc;n lửa h\u0026agrave;nh tr\u0026igrave;nh SOM-J,\u003c/strong\u003e sản phẩm \u0026quot;Made in T\u0026uuml;rkiye\u0026quot; từ b\u0026agrave;n tay t\u0026agrave;i hoa của T\u0026Uuml;BİTAK SAGE v\u0026agrave; Roketsan, đại diện cho bước nhảy vọt trong c\u0026ocirc;ng nghệ vũ kh\u0026iacute; chống hạm.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eVới thiết kế m\u0026ocirc;-đun gọn nhẹ, \u003cstrong\u003et\u0026ecirc;n lửa SOM-J\u003c/strong\u003e được tối ưu h\u0026oacute;a để mang theo tr\u0026ecirc;n c\u0026aacute;c nền tảng h\u0026agrave;ng kh\u0026ocirc;ng hiện đại như \u003cstrong\u003eF-16, F-35\u003c/strong\u003e hay thậm ch\u0026iacute; \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/may-bay-quan-su-tag385.epi\"\u003em\u0026aacute;y bay chiến đấu\u003c/a\u003e kh\u0026ocirc;ng người l\u0026aacute;i \u003cstrong\u003e(UCAV),\u003c/strong\u003e gi\u0026uacute;p lực lượng kh\u0026ocirc;ng qu\u0026acirc;n Thổ Nhĩ Kỳ linh hoạt hơn bao giờ hết trong c\u0026aacute;c sứ mệnh tấn c\u0026ocirc;ng tầm xa.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eChiều d\u0026agrave;i chỉ vỏn vẹn 3.9 m\u0026eacute;t v\u0026agrave; khối lượng ph\u0026oacute;ng khoảng 540kg, \u003cstrong\u003et\u0026ecirc;n lửa SOM-J\u003c/strong\u003e dễ d\u0026agrave;ng t\u0026iacute;ch hợp dưới c\u0026aacute;nh hoặc trong khoang m\u0026aacute;y bay, giảm thiểu g\u0026aacute;nh nặng cho phi cơ m\u0026agrave; vẫn đảm bảo sức hủy diệt khủng khiếp.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eVề th\u0026ocirc;ng số kỹ thuật, \u003cstrong\u003et\u0026ecirc;n lửa SOM-J\u003c/strong\u003e sở hữu tầm bắn ấn tượng từ 200 đến 275km, cho ph\u0026eacute;p n\u0026oacute; \u0026quot;vươn tay\u0026quot; đ\u0026aacute;nh ch\u0026igrave;m \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/tau-chien-tag1655.epi\"\u003et\u0026agrave;u chiến\u003c/a\u003e địch m\u0026agrave; kh\u0026ocirc;ng cần tiếp cận gần, giảm rủi ro cho phi c\u0026ocirc;ng.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eTốc độ bay cao dưới \u0026acirc;m thanh (high subsonic) gi\u0026uacute;p t\u0026ecirc;n lửa duy tr\u0026igrave; sự b\u0026iacute; mật, kết hợp với khả năng bay theo địa h\u0026igrave;nh (terrain-following) v\u0026agrave; đặc biệt l\u0026agrave; chế độ bay s\u0026aacute;t mặt biển (sea-skimming) ở độ cao cực thấp – chỉ v\u0026agrave;i m\u0026eacute;t tr\u0026ecirc;n mặt nước.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url(\u0027https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:346px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"Ti\u0026ecirc;m k\u0026iacute;ch F-16 ph\u0026oacute;ng t\u0026ecirc;n lửa SOM-J. (Ảnh chụp m\u0026agrave;n h\u0026igrave;nh từ video bắn thử/navalnews.com).\" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"346\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eTi\u0026ecirc;m k\u0026iacute;ch F-16 ph\u0026oacute;ng t\u0026ecirc;n lửa SOM-J. (Ảnh chụp m\u0026agrave;n h\u0026igrave;nh từ video bắn thử/navalnews.com).\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eNhờ đ\u0026oacute;, \u003cstrong\u003et\u0026ecirc;n lửa SOM-J\u003c/strong\u003e c\u0026oacute; thể \u0026quot;lẩn trốn\u0026quot; radar đối phương, thực hiện c\u0026aacute;c c\u0026uacute; ngoặt n\u0026eacute; tr\u0026aacute;nh hệ thống ph\u0026ograve;ng thủ ti\u0026ecirc;n tiến, như đ\u0026atilde; chứng minh trong thử nghiệm gần đ\u0026acirc;y khi n\u0026oacute; lao qua m\u0026ocirc;i trường biển phức tạp m\u0026agrave; kh\u0026ocirc;ng bị ph\u0026aacute;t hiện.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eHệ thống dẫn đường của \u003cstrong\u003et\u0026ecirc;n lửa SOM-J\u003c/strong\u003e l\u0026agrave; \u0026quot;bộ n\u0026atilde;o\u0026quot; thực thụ, kết hợp định vị qu\u0026aacute;n t\u0026iacute;nh (INS) chống nhiễu, GPS chống jamming, dẫn đường theo địa h\u0026igrave;nh (TRN), dẫn đường địa h\u0026igrave;nh to\u0026agrave;n cầu (GRNS) v\u0026agrave; bộ t\u0026igrave;m kiếm hồng ngoại h\u0026igrave;nh ảnh (IIR) ở giai đoạn cuối.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eĐiểm nhấn l\u0026agrave; li\u0026ecirc;n kết dữ liệu mạng (datalink) cho ph\u0026eacute;p cập nhật mục ti\u0026ecirc;u thời gian thực, thậm ch\u0026iacute; hỗ trợ tấn c\u0026ocirc;ng phối hợp với c\u0026aacute;c vũ kh\u0026iacute; kh\u0026aacute;c.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eĐầu đạn nặng 140kg loại nổ mảnh cao (high-explosive fragmentation) hoặc xuy\u0026ecirc;n gi\u0026aacute;p (semi-armor-piercing) đủ sức v\u0026ocirc; hiệu h\u0026oacute;a t\u0026agrave;u khu trục cỡ trung, biến \u003cstrong\u003et\u0026ecirc;n lửa SOM-J\u003c/strong\u003e th\u0026agrave;nh \u0026quot;người h\u0026ugrave;ng\u0026quot; trong c\u0026aacute;c cuộc t\u0026aacute;c chiến hiện đại tại eo biển Aegean hay Biển Đen.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eCuộc thử nghiệm bắn đạn thật ng\u0026agrave;y 13/10 từ F-16 đ\u0026atilde; ghi dấu ấn lịch sử: t\u0026ecirc;n lửa SOM-J t\u0026aacute;ch khỏi m\u0026aacute;y bay, lao xuống độ cao sea-skimming, duy tr\u0026igrave; h\u0026agrave;nh tr\u0026igrave;nh thấp v\u0026agrave; kết th\u0026uacute;c bằng đ\u0026ograve;n đ\u0026aacute;nh ch\u0026iacute;nh x\u0026aacute;c v\u0026agrave;o mục ti\u0026ecirc;u biển cố định.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eĐ\u0026acirc;y kh\u0026ocirc;ng chỉ l\u0026agrave; minh chứng cho sự trưởng th\u0026agrave;nh của c\u0026ocirc;ng nghệ nội địa Thổ Nhĩ Kỳ m\u0026agrave; c\u0026ograve;n mở đường cho xuất khẩu, gi\u0026uacute;p Ankara giảm phụ thuộc v\u0026agrave;o nguồn cung nước ngo\u0026agrave;i v\u0026agrave; củng cố vị thế trong NATO.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url(\u0027https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png\u0027)] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\"\u003e\n   \u003ci class\u003d\"icon font-[\u0027bm-font-icon\u0027] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\n   \u003cbutton class\u003d\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style\u003d\"width:625px;height:416px\"\u003e\n    \u003cpicture\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/avif\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003csource srcset\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" type\u003d\"image/webp\"\u003e\u003c/source\u003e\n     \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"T\u0026ecirc;n lửa h\u0026agrave;nh tr\u0026igrave;nh SOM-J. (Nguồn ảnh: Roketsan)\" width\u003d\"625\" height\u003d\"416\" /\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eT\u0026ecirc;n lửa h\u0026agrave;nh tr\u0026igrave;nh SOM-J. (Nguồn ảnh: Roketsan)\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026Yacute; nghĩa chiến lược\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eT\u0026ecirc;n lửa h\u0026agrave;nh tr\u0026igrave;nh SOM-J\u003c/strong\u003e kh\u0026ocirc;ng chỉ l\u0026agrave; một bước tiến c\u0026ocirc;ng nghệ m\u0026agrave; c\u0026ograve;n mang \u0026yacute; nghĩa chiến lược then chốt đối với Thổ Nhĩ Kỳ, khẳng định vị thế của Ankara như một cường quốc \u003ca class\u003d\"tag-link\" href\u003d\"/the-gioi.epi\"\u003equ\u0026acirc;n sự\u003c/a\u003e tự chủ trong bối cảnh căng thẳng tại Địa Trung Hải v\u0026agrave; Biển Đen.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eVới khả năng tấn c\u0026ocirc;ng ch\u0026iacute;nh x\u0026aacute;c tầm xa l\u0026ecirc;n đến 275km từ c\u0026aacute;c nền tảng h\u0026agrave;ng kh\u0026ocirc;ng như F-16 hay F-35, \u003cstrong\u003et\u0026ecirc;n lửa SOM-J\u003c/strong\u003e đ\u0026oacute;ng vai tr\u0026ograve; \u0026quot;nh\u0026acirc;n tố nh\u0026acirc;n l\u0026ecirc;n sức mạnh\u0026quot; (force multiplier) cho Lực lượng Vũ trang Thổ Nhĩ Kỳ, cho ph\u0026eacute;p v\u0026ocirc; hiệu h\u0026oacute;a c\u0026aacute;c mục ti\u0026ecirc;u hải qu\u0026acirc;n cao gi\u0026aacute; trị m\u0026agrave; kh\u0026ocirc;ng cần tiếp cận gần, giảm thiểu rủi ro cho phi cơ v\u0026agrave; phi c\u0026ocirc;ng trong m\u0026ocirc;i trường t\u0026aacute;c chiến hiện đại.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text\"\u003eĐồng thời, việc ph\u0026aacute;t triển nội địa bởi T\u0026Uuml;BİTAK SAGE v\u0026agrave; Roketsan củng cố chiến lược tự chủ c\u0026ocirc;ng nghệ, gi\u0026uacute;p Thổ Nhĩ Kỳ giảm phụ thuộc v\u0026agrave;o nguồn cung vũ kh\u0026iacute; nước ngo\u0026agrave;i, tăng cường khả năng răn đe chống lại c\u0026aacute;c mối đe dọa từ Hy Lạp, Cyprus hay c\u0026aacute;c thế lực khu vực, đồng thời mở ra tiềm năng xuất khẩu để n\u0026acirc;ng cao ảnh hưởng ngoại giao v\u0026agrave; kinh tế quốc ph\u0026ograve;ng.\u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003cp class\u003d\"text body-author text-right\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e Đ\u0026agrave;o Cảnh \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n \u003c/div\u003e\n \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp\" tabindex\u003d\"-1\" role\u003d\"dialog\" aria-hidden\u003d\"true\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__bg\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__scroll-wrap\"\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__container\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__item\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003c/div\u003e\n   \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__top-bar\"\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__counter\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title\u003d\"Close (Esc)\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--share\" title\u003d\"Share\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--fs\" title\u003d\"Toggle fullscreen\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cbutton type\u003d\"button\" class\u003d\"pswp__button pswp__button--zoom\" title\u003d\"Zoom in/out\"\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n     \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__icn\"\u003e\n       \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__cut\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__preloader__donut\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n       \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n     \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class\u003d\"pswp__share-modal ps